'''热带风暴诺曼'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Norman}}）是2006年10月在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]西南部降下暴雨的一个弱[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是[[2006年太平洋飓风季|2006年太平洋飓风季]]第12场获命名的风暴，于10月9日经墨西哥西南方向较远处海域的[[东风波|东风波]]发展而成。由于外界环境很快变得不利，诺曼仅成型两天后便完全消散热带气旋。不久后，气旋中心变得杂乱无章，很快便再度消散，产生的大范围湿气令其残留转向东面前进。受东侧的[[热带扰动|扰动天气区]]影响，风暴残留关联的[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动再度增长，于10月15日在墨西哥近海重新成为墨西哥西南部的降雨量达到150毫米。约有150套房屋被风暴降下的雨水淹没，其中约20套被毁。该国有一人受伤，另有报导称两人失踪，但消息之后没有得到证实。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Norman 2006 track.png}}
9月21日，有[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西海岸，穿越[[大西洋|大西洋]]和[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]期间没有显著发展。10月1日，东风波进入东[[太平洋|太平洋]]并继续西进，于10月5日发展出持续的[[对流|对流区]]。<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | date = 2006-11-30 | title = Tropical Storm Norman Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002014419/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP152006_Norman.pdf | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-08-13 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP152006_Norman.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>天气系统起初杂乱无章，但气象机构认为上层大气环境会变得有利于热带气旋形成，预计系统也会逐渐发展<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Blake | author2 = Pasch | date = 2006-10-06 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2016-08-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160813035932/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2006/TWOEP.200610062215.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2006/TWOEP.200610062215.txt | archivedate = 2016-08-13 | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>。10月7日，系统发展出广阔的[[低气压|低气压区]]<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Blake | author2 = Pasch | date = 2006-10-06 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160813040210/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2006/TWOEP.200610070334.txt | accessdate = 2016-08-13 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2006/TWOEP.200610070334.txt | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-08-13 | format = TXT }}</ref>，到次日时已位移至大范围扰动天气区的东部，系统的西部之后发展成[[2006年太平洋颶風季#热带风暴奥利维亚|热带风暴奥利维亚]]，东部则在中心附近发展出井井有条的对流，于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]10月9日在[[下加利福尼亞半島|下加利福尼亞半島]]最南端的西南方向约1235公里洋面发展成第十五{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。

成为热带气旋后，低气压围绕弱[[高压脊|高压脊]]的西部边缘朝西北偏北方向移动，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]在针对气旋发布的首份公告中预计热带低气压会逐渐增强，然后在穿越[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]]期间逐渐减弱<ref name="disc1">{{cite report | author1 = Rhome | author2 = Pasch | date = 2006-10-09 | title = Tropical Depression Fifteen Special Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160317232314/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-17 }}</ref>。由于所在洋面[[海面温度|水温]]较高，气旋中心附近发展出有组织的深层对流，气象卫星采用[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]估算系统风速已达热带风暴强度，美国国家飓风中心因此将成型仅12小时的热带低气压升级成热带风暴，并以“诺曼”（{{lang|en|Norman}}）命名<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 2006-10-09 | title = Tropical Storm Norman Discussion Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-13 | archivedate = 2016-03-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160317223447/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.003.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.003.shtml? | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴继续强化，于10月10日达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]85公里的最高强度<ref name="tcr" />。气象部门当时认为诺曼会继续向东北前进并增强，但也有部分[[热带气旋预测模型|飓风预测模型]]预测气旋会向东南大幅转向并迅速减弱<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Rhome | author2 = Pasch | date = 2006-10-09 | title = Tropical Storm Norman Discussion Five | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-13 | archivedate = 2016-03-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160317193438/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.005.shtml? }}</ref>。达到最高强度后不久，西南向[[风切变|风切变]]出现增长，导致风暴对流的覆盖面缩小。与此同时，从[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]向南延伸的[[低压槽|低压槽]]导致诺曼的移动速度放缓并转向东进<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Knabb | author2 = Willis | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160318075039/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.006.shtml | date = 2006-10-09 | title = Tropical Storm Norman Discussion Six | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-13 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.006.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-18 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。对流快速同中心分离，到10月10日晚，中心同最近的雷暴已相隔185公里。气旋此时已降级成[[热带气旋等级|热带低气压]]<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Roberts | author2 = Franklin | date = 2006-10-09 | title = Tropical Depression Norman Discussion Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160317191331/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.008.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.008.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，再于10月11日在下加利福尼亚半岛最南端的[[卡波圣卢卡斯|卡波圣卢卡斯]]（{{lang|en|Cabo San Lucas}}）西南方向约855公里洋面退化成残留低气压区<ref name="tcr" />。

诺曼的残留继续向东行进，之后受墨西哥近海的热带扰动影响转向东南偏东<ref name="tcr" />。气象机构起初没有料到气旋会在热带扰动的影响下重生<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy Stewart | date = 2006-10-12 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-13 | archivedate = 2016-08-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160813083916/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2006/TWOEP.200610121013.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2006/TWOEP.200610121013.txt | deadurl = no | format = TXT }}</ref>。10月13日，美国国家飓风中心称诺曼的残留正在同东侧的扰动天气合并<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Mainelli | author2 = Beven | date = 2006-10-13 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2008-08-29 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2006/TWOEP.200610131019.txt | format = TXT | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160813084113/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2006/TWOEP.200610131019.txt | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-08-13 }}</ref>，受其影响，残留低气压区周围重新发展出对流并逐渐组织，于10月15日清晨在墨西哥西南近海再生成热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。由于水温较高，上层大气环境有利，气象部门预计诺曼会再度达到热带风暴强度并[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | date = 2006-10-09 | title = Tropical Depression Norman Discussion Ten | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-13 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.010.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303211731/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.010.shtml }}</ref>。但是，气旋中心的组织结构实际上很快就变得混乱<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Brown | author2 = Knabb | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160318011429/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.011.shtml | date = 2006-10-09 | title = Tropical Depression Norman Discussion Eleven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2008-08-30 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep15/ep152006.discus.011.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-18 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，并在大范围的热带扰动内部转向北上，之后又转朝西北方向移动。据美国国家飓风中心估计，热带低气压诺曼于10月15日晚在[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]以南约37公里近海完全消散，但卫星图像表明气旋中心有可能是在陆地上空消散<ref name="tcr" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Tropical_Depression_Norman_(2006).PNG|right]]

诺曼再度发展成热带气旋时，墨西哥政府向[[拉萨罗卡德纳斯|拉萨罗卡德纳斯]]到卡布科连特斯（{{lang|en|Cabo Corrientes}}）发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref name="tcr" />。

风暴在墨西哥西南部降下暴雨，其中以[[米却肯州|米却肯州]]的拉维利塔（{{lang|en|La Villita}}）降雨量最高，达161毫米<ref>{{cite report | author = Servicio Meteorológico Nacional | year = 2006 | title = Resumen de la Tormenta Tropical "Norman" Del Océano Pacífico | accessdate = 2008-08-31 | format = PDF | archivedate = 2007-06-25 | deadurl = yes | url = http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2006/pacifico/norman/norman.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070625122426/http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2006/pacifico/norman/norman.pdf | date =  }}</ref>。持续四天的降水促使政府官员将[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]及周边的学校关闭，还导致树木倒塌和多起[[泥石流|泥石流]]。约有150幢民宅被淹，军方人员出动协助人员撤离<ref name="elun" />。墨西哥共有20套民房被毁，20个村庄停电<ref name="lajo">{{cite news |author=La Journada |date=2006-10-17 |title=Desbordan lluvias ríos en Guerrero |accessdate=2013-01-12 |url=http://www.elporvenir.com.mx/notas.asp?nota_id=91242 |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20130112044312/http://www.elporvenir.com.mx/notas.asp?nota_id=91242 |archivedate=2013-01-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。一辆载有15人的运输车被急流卷走，致使一人受伤，车辆之后获警方救援<ref name="elun" />。约有300公顷农田受到破坏<ref name="lajo" />，但由于此时收割季节已过，因此实际损失的农作物很少<ref name="elun">{{cite news | author = Juan Cervantes Gómez | publisher = El Universal | date = 2006-10-16 | title = Suspenden clases en Acapulco por tormenta tropical "Norman" | accessdate = 2016-08-13 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305011938/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/381709.html | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/381709.html }}</ref>。墨西哥全国共有约50万人受到诺曼影响，起初还有报导声称两人失踪<ref name="lajo" />，但之后的报导又表明风暴没有导致人员伤亡<ref name="tcr" />。

